data.description: Come home to this fully fenced five acre property featuring sprawling pastures, a 32x32 double-car garage/workshop, and a 1,246 Sq. Ft. single level home with end-of-road privacy. The house presents a 3 bedroom layout plus living areas graced with warm-toned finishes. You will certainly find solace in the master bedroom which comes with great closet space and a lovely private bathroom. Both the shared and en-suite bathrooms are generous in size and boast a sink, toilet, and tub/shower. You will love the eat-in kitchen that truly sets the tone for relaxed living; featuring ample cupboard storage, lots of bench space, new flooring, and warm pendant lighting. Adjacent to this is the living room offering the perfect place to relax or host guests. Radon: Well Log Available This space flows out to the deck offering views of the Bitterroot Mountains. The laundry doubles as a mud room creating the perfect transition space between the inside and the outdoors. This home also boasts a new roof in 2020.
